32 Sec. 8. 8 MRSA §381-A is enacted to read:
33 §381-A. Bulk purchase of tickets or shares prohibited
34 1. Bulk purchase; definition. As used in this section, unless the context otherwise
35 indicates, "bulk purchase" means the purchase, in aggregate, of tickets or shares in a lottery
36 game in an amount exceeding $100,000 that:
37 A. Occurs in a single transaction or multiple transactions;
38 B. Is made at a single retail location or multiple retail locations; and
39 C. Is made by an individual or multiple individuals acting in concert.
